Validation of  Login Credentials
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 	http://senchatouch2.firstfreight.com/ajax.aspx?fn=1
 	usr: demo@example.com 
 	pwd: demo

 	On Successful Login
 		Goto Dashboard.aspx - Authenticated Demo Landing Page
 		
	On Unsuccessful Login
		Popup Message - ( Username or password are not valid )

Forgot Password
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 	1) Popup to Enter Email (you@yourcompany.com)
 	2) Will send demo usr/pwd to any email entered 		
 	
Remember Me
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	1) Store usr/pwd on local device - encrypted
	2) Login page load - populate usr/pwd & checkbox

Security
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	1) Validate Best-Practices for Athentication & Performance
	
